SO5Pg">Thập nguyệt nhất nhật - 十月一日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-Tam-Hi%E1%BB%87p/poem-Y05iwnYWNPzh38KdWy5UUw">Thướng Tam Hiệp - 上三峽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/Tu%E1%BA%A7n-th%E1%BB%8B-Ch%C3%A2n-%C4%90%C4%83ng-ch%C3%A2u/poem-A9d3W-TENBDMfeekikcTYQ">Tuần thị Chân Đăng châu - 巡視真登州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-ho%C3%A0i-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-tsbQj4HVt-8QHPeUfTCzPg">Vịnh hoài kỳ 1 - 詠懷其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-H%C3%A0nh/V%C5%A9-h%E1%BA%ADu-%C4%91%C4%83ng-Hu%E1%BB%87-s%C6%A1n-t%E1%BB%91i-cao-%C4%91%E1%BB%89nh/poem-O8Mn5ENbb9kzEwKMGHdNtg">Vũ hậu đăng Huệ sơn tối cao đỉnh - 雨後登惠山最高頂</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87u-Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-H%C3%A0nh/author-5lgSjN7ZZCZyfUZzbDgkng">Thiệu Trường Hành</a>)<br></div>	</div>
